data.description: Live in the wonderful Emerald Bay gated community in this tastefully updated home.  Featuring just under 4000 sq ft, the home is a 4 bdrm/ 3 1/2 bath property.  It additionally features an office off the master.  The master and another spacious bedroom and bath are downstairs.  Upstairs features 2 more bedrooms and a bath.  One of these bedrooms is large enough to be a gameroom.   Additional features include  a 2 car garage with golf cart area and a lovely backyard including a separate garden area and green house. Emerald Bay homeowners enjoy golf, tennis, swimming,fishing, boating, and a secure environment with a staffed guard gate and 24/7 security.   For more information about Emerald Bay, visit the Emerald Bay club website.
